&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About BEES&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us to build the future of B2B commerce!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BEES is AB InBev’s B2B platform. Through our ecosystem,&amp;nbsp;merchants&amp;nbsp;and retailers across 29 countries can stock their businesses quickly, easily, and securely.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;At BEES, we dream big, lead with purpose, and develop technology that transforms the way retailers and sellers grow.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every line of code and every partnership is built in service of a single mission: to make commerce better for retailers and sellers around the world. Here, your work is not&amp;nbsp;just important. It makes a difference!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, maintain, and support backend applications and services using Java and Spring Boot;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the development of RESTful APIs, microservices, and system integrations under the guidance of senior team members;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality solutions aligned with business needs;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in code reviews, testing activities, and continuous improvement initiatives;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor application performance and help troubleshoot issues in production and non-production environments;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow engineering best practices related to code quality, testing, documentation, and automation;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to CI/CD processes and support cloud-native and containerized applications using technologies such as Docker and Kubernetes;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously learn and apply new technologies, tools, and development practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for people with:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;University degree in Computer Science, Computer Engineering, Information Systems, Systems Analysis and Development, or related fields;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience or academic projects involving backend development with Java;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of RESTful APIs and object-oriented programming principles;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Spring Framework technologies such as Spring Boot, Spring MVC, or Spring Security;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of software development fundamentals, including data structures, algorithms, and design patterns;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of software testing concepts such as unit and integration testing;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to cloud platforms, Docker, Kubernetes, or DevOps practices is a plus;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working on team projects, internships, trainee programs, or Agile environments is a plus;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intermediate English communication skills, both written and spoken;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical thinking and problem-solving skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who should apply?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re passionate about software development and eager to learn and grow your technical skills;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re motivated by building solutions that create value and impact for users;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re curious, proactive, and open to receiving feedback and mentoring;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You enjoy solving problems and continuously looking for ways to improve processes and applications;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You communicate effectively and collaborate well with teammates from different backgrounds;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You take ownership of your tasks and are committed to delivering high-quality work;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You&#39;re excited to work in a fast-paced environment and learn modern software engineering practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
