&lt;p class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot; data-start=&quot;261&quot; data-end=&quot;484&quot;&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;BEES Strategic Growth Specialist&lt;/strong&gt;, you will play a key role in driving market share growth through data-driven strategies and AI-powered solutions. This position focuses on identifying the highest-value customer opportunities, developing scalable methodologies across markets, and enabling commercial teams to outperform competitors by expanding market penetration and strengthening customer engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
