&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with Marketplace, Product, Data, and country teams to scale best practices and accelerate volume growth across markets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present business results, insights, and recommendations to senior leadership, supporting strategic decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
